00:00:30,080 --> 00:00:31,530
常识告诉我们，
It's reasonable to assume

11
00:00:31,530 --> 00:00:34,894
水库的容量取决于拦截它的大坝，
a reservoir can only be as big as the dam that created it,

12
00:00:34,893 --> 00:00:37,561
这就是为什么工程团队
which is why teams here are having to pull off

13
00:00:37,561 --> 00:00:39,417
必须先完成一项罕见而艰难的任务。
a rare and difficult task first.

14
00:00:39,417 --> 00:00:44,480
他们要在原有大坝的基础上，再建一座新坝。
They're expanding the dam itself by building a new one on top of it.

15
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:46,653
>> 这真的是世界上第一次
>> Well, this is really the first time

16
00:00:46,653 --> 00:00:49,912
