One that's already seen this gigantic scheme stopped in its tracks.

21
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:13,360
说到科罗拉多，你脑海中浮现的大概就是这样的画面。
Think Colorado, and you'll probably imagine something like this.

22
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:17,419
丹佛郊外便是落基山脉的起点，
Just outside Denver is where the Rocky Mountains begin

23
00:01:17,419 --> 00:01:19,934
这里拥有丰沛的水资源。
and where a great deal of water can be found.

24
00:01:19,934 --> 00:01:25,855
湖泊、水库、科罗拉多河及其支流，触手可及。
There are lakes, reservoirs, the Colorado River, and its tributaries, all within reach.

25
00:01:25,855 --> 00:01:28,549
如果你向往宁静的生活，这里再合适不过。
It's a good place to be if you like the quiet life.

26
00:01:28,549 --> 00:01:31,522
只有这处特定的地点例外——
Except that is for this particular site,

27
00:01:31,522 --> 00:01:35,388
近年来，这里已经成了一个热火朝天的工地。
which has become a hive of activity in recent years.

28
00:01:35,388 --> 00:01:36,591
上世纪五十年代，
Back in the 1950s,

29
00:01:36,591 --> 00:01:41,468
为了服务丹佛都会区，这里修建了一座大型重力坝。
a large gravity dam was built here to serve the Denver metropolitan area.

30
00:01:41,468 --> 00:01:43,127
随着人口不断增长，
Due to its rising population,

31
00:01:43,127 --> 00:01:45,072
